iteria led to an over-abundance of\ngalaxies with close massive companions, we do not find any significant\ninfluence of the presence or absence of a close companion on the relative\nstrength of the nuclear H alpha peak, nor on the H alpha morphology around the\nnucleus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Nov 2005 14:02:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
